devdoc.details: A contract to demonstrate knowledge of control structures in Solidity.

AfterHours(uint256).details: A custom error to indicate that an operation was attempted after hours.

params._time: The time at which the operation was attempted.
The time to check, in 24-hour format (e.g., 1300 for 1:00 PM).

returns._0: A string memory representing the time of day.
